title: Supernatural Nevada - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/15/22

description:
George Noory and paranormal investigator Joshua P. Warren explore his research into strange events around Nevada, including Area 51, a time warp near Las Vegas, reports of a mysterious creature escaping from an underground military base, and his own plans to build a portal to access other dimensions.
